    <j.2:build_info>cdm:CDM_3.2.3  tdm:1523  xslt:3945 saxon:9.0.0.1J JVM:1.6.0_29 metaconvJar:5.6.0 builddate:25/06/2015 18:14:51</j.2:build_info>
